56
00:04:59,050 --> 00:05:00,020
Outlier.

57
00:05:01,030 --> 00:05:03,760
How could our Bai family have an outlier like you?

58
00:05:08,230 --> 00:05:11,560
Rumors at the Intelligence Bureau say my grandson

59
00:05:12,330 --> 00:05:14,540
has lost control over a target

60
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:16,560
and has even fallen in love with him!

61
00:05:16,570 --> 00:05:18,850
And now you've even taken a bullet for such a person!

62
00:05:18,850 --> 00:05:20,050
What kind of person?

63
00:05:23,570 --> 00:05:25,260
Grandpa, you've never seen Hei

64
00:05:25,260 --> 00:05:26,790
and don't understand him.

65
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,960
How can you deny everything about him

66
00:05:28,960 --> 00:05:30,150
just because he's on the other side?

67
00:05:30,150 --> 00:05:33,550
Since ancient times, good and evil have always been enemies.

68
00:05:33,590 --> 00:05:34,720
People like him are a threat

69
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:35,580
and the source of chaos.

70
00:05:35,580 --> 00:05:37,110
They shouldn't even exist!

71
00:05:38,190 --> 00:05:39,320
Hei is the most loyal

72
00:05:39,370 --> 00:05:41,240
and kind-hearted person I've ever met!

73
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:42,409
Still talking back?

74
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:47,070
This is the first time in our family's history

75
00:05:47,070 --> 00:05:49,740
that someone has been suspended as punishment.

76
00:05:50,460 --> 00:05:51,990
What a disgrace!

77
00:05:53,350 --> 00:05:55,980
Grandpa, stop clinging to those outdated ways of thinking!

78
00:05:55,980 --> 00:05:57,710
You think you're clear-headed

79
00:05:57,940 --> 00:05:59,770
about right and wrong, but you're not!

80
